{"tid":436194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【被拍片瘋傳】台靚女主播疑洗霸王頭 「丟臉丟到泰國去」","createTime":"2017-10-15T03:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T19:31:49.000Z","uid":34252,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"47fd937fe565ac26e1dc92b040ab9a1f45ef053a","tid":436194,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"台灣女主播偕閨密赴泰國旅遊，疑似因為洗頭不付錢，被店家全程直播，鬧上當地媒體！粉絲團逾11萬粉絲的寰宇新聞台主播黃若薇，在曼谷Siam Square一間髮型屋消費，事後卻不願付費。沙龍老闆聞訊趕到後，示意員工開直播，影片被放上fb，過程長達12分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n影片中，黃若薇及友人在店內不停講電話、玩手機，髮型屋老闆眼看已超過打烊時間近一小時，叫10多名員工先下班，他留下處理。老闆質疑，黃若薇已完成洗髮，為何不付錢？黃的友人則相當介意她們不能離開，雙方雞同鴨嘴，毫無交集。過程中，黃若薇欲錄影，被老闆打掉手機。<br />\n<br />\n僵持過後，黃的閨密率先下樓，黃若薇跟着出門被擋下，最後付錢了事，離開現場。影片在泰國迅速蔓延，泰網友還一度以為兩女是中國人。消息傳回台灣，被網友把影片分享至fb社團「爆廢公社」，留言一面倒大罵黃若薇及其閨密，「只為了250泰銖（約59港元）有必要這麼計較嗎？」、「台灣人名聲被妳們搞臭」、「丟臉丟到泰國去」。<br />\n<br />\n黃若薇今晨4點在粉絲團PO文，解釋是店家坐地起價，預約價250泰銖，洗完頭卻變成350泰銖（約83港元）；沒冷氣就算了，還用冷水洗頭。她朋友因擔心感冒，僅沖濕髮尾就不洗了，沒想到店家要收原價，她們才不肯付費。<br />\n<br />\n只是網友駡聲排山倒海，有網友提供中文翻譯質疑黃若薇的說法，指店家沒有要收她朋友錢、黃的費用折扣後250泰銖，都與黃所言不符。黃若薇文末表示，她自我反省，「我們也有口氣不佳的地方，部分內容與事實有出入，對我們不公平，這件事情我認為雙方都有不對！」<br />\n<br />\n她並為不夠了解當地民情致歉，「真的很對不起，出國在外我應該更謹慎，也謝謝各位的留言。」<br />\n<br />\n台灣最美的風景不是人嗎?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Krz-LEHKbBg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKrz-LEHKbBg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=lIJcOy1SdpiccVNprGOqLcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=63e64b16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Krz-LEHKbBg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"e0673882eff3703b5c02939e0b2f43e130c9e0d2","tid":436194,"uid":51904,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"女主播黃若薇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2726/d2726875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2726%2Fd2726875.jpg&h=dd951e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/O3E35z1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO3E35z1.jpg&h=85c23ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170121/420_65659384d7151b691c29b3ba09c915fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170121%2F420_65659384d7151b691c29b3ba09c915fc.jpg&h=6106d73a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9f6792295a23c5e48d22d9c27df648999724d6d","tid":436194,"uid":81150,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"個波大到咁都唔俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1355612f4428c44474d486e9f094177df8764a07","tid":436194,"uid":6086,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女主播黃若薇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2726/d2726875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2726%2Fd2726875.jpg&h=dd951e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/O3E35z1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO3E35z1.jpg&h=85c23ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170121/420_65659384d7151b691c29b3ba09c915fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170121%2F420_65659384d7151b691c29b3ba09c915fc.jpg&h=6106d73a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa9b9806b3c74ef12628ac86fc98ea7d7599328","tid":436194,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT